calibrate.subtitle.message: Calibrating XSplit VCam allows us to improve the performance for you environment and camera.

calibrate.vidConsent.message: Upload a 15s video and calibration data for improving performance

calibrate.subtitle2.message: Stay in front of your camera for 15 seconds, look to the sides, raise your arms, or do what you usually do on camera.

calibrate.subtitle3.message: XSplit VCam is now ready. Just select "XSplit VCam" as your camera in Skype, OBS, XSplit Broadcaster or any other application that uses a camera.

calibrate.denyConsent.message: Are you sure you don't want to upload your calibration data? We will ONLY use your data to improve the background removal AI, without it we cannot improve your experience.

feedback.ask.message: How do you like our app?

feedback.rating.low.message: We're sorry you're having a bad time.

feedback.vidConsent.message: I want to record a sample video

feedback.question.message: Is there anything else we could improve? Feature requests?

feedback.assurance.message: We'll be working on improving your experience.
